input.nextLine() takes the Scanner to the next line of input, but input.nextDouble() does not. Therefore, you&#39;ll need to either advance the Scanner to the next line:

```
            price = input.nextDouble();
            input.nextLine();
```

Or, you can use nextLine() directly instead and parse that into a Double:

```
            price = Double.parseDouble(input.nextLine());
```

